node.text: Thanks to all my fans, my team and ... me :)
Playing football on the rest day, after 4 rounds, here in London. More behind the scenes, live feeds and updates on @playmagnus’ Facebook.

node.text:
This photo was just begging for a caption competition. Show us what you’ve got! I'll wisely wait till after the World Championship match.

Photo credit: @norway_chess

It’s all over for another year! This year’s @playmagnus #PlayLiveChallenge was a tremendous success yet again. I wanted to thank all the contestants for traveling so far to play against me, and our sponsors @spiegel.online.de, WorldQuant, @chessbasegmbh and Grenke for making it all happen.

node.text: Four years, two cities and 36 challengers later - and I still haven’t been beaten. Think you’ll be the one to finally defeat me at the ‪#PlayLiveChallenge‬ this year? Start racking up your points in the ‪@PlayMagnus‬ app and you might just get the chance!

node.text: "Tilbudet har blitt mye bedre siden i fjor" sier TV2s turorienterings-ekspert Jon Ludvig Hammer. "Før lå postene gjerne på koller. Nå finner man dem i skrenter, samt på myrer og steiner"
